    "This interpolation operates purely in space and is applied independently at each timestep.",
    "Next, u 0:L-1 (Ξ) is passed through a causal convolutional network that encodes the data in both space and time (section D.1.2), yielding latent tokens Z 0:Le-1 of length L e < L when temporal compression is used.",
    "Temporal compression is optional, for notation simplicity, we will assume we do not compress time dimension.",
    "These latent tokens form the input to the autoregressive dynamics model.",
    "The decoder mirrors the encoder's structure."
